{"tid":1932531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國勇撤回文章，請視為港版吹哨人","createTime":"2020-03-18T19:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T09:03:54.000Z","uid":286309,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43af95bfe79bd2bd705848aac2b95dcb16553623","tid":1932531,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"我相信篇文章已經達到左目的<br />\n<br />\n現家後續要做嘅<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">就係帶風向</span></strong></em><br />\n<br />\n首先將袁國類比為支那嘅吹哨人醫生<br />\n<br />\n兩者同樣指出真相，然後被政權禁聲<br />\n<br />\n將此事連同中共趕走美籍記者<br />\n<br />\n請各位帶風向，洗版<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「所有醫生，中國都要打壓」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「指出真相永遠在中國是罪」</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔撚係Blame The Victim呀<br />\n咁撚好張牌都唔識用?</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"9a0ec7eeffcbd3aab7f2bd502821ba00a9aaa564","tid":1932531,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T19:41:47.000Z","msg":"同時間響啲淺藍圈度散播極端言論<br />\n用最紅批鬥人唔夠紅<br />\n<br />\n例如去啲香討baby condom果啲<br />\n講話<br />\n袁國勇正漢奸 而家中國向全世界講話隻毒係美國製 就算佢知道來源係中國 都唔應該講返真話出黎 倒中國米 正曱甴<br />\n<br />\n然後再搵啲人入去引罵戰<br />\n等啲藍屍短腦<br />\n啲淺藍或者有機轉軚"},{"pid":"9aed0f4401aa2589b64fd728d485a4d001da2ffc","tid":1932531,"uid":171742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span>"},{"pid":"173f12dc1497bc5e1d21cdd7051fa54cff5fc6d0","tid":1932531,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:03:00.000Z","msg":"日日推呢篇文"},{"pid":"d21e0a3149a234a80c6c9f075f49bb9dd8c761d0","tid":1932531,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"